Several pull requests have been made to the elizaOS/eliza repository recently:

1. PR #4403 by madjin updates documentation, changing to docs.eliza.how

2. PR #4407 by 0xbbjoker adds a new feature for plugin integration with OpenRouter

3. PR #4404 by noraldase is simply titled 'pull' without further details

4. PR #4406 by 0xbbjoker removes the plugin-browser from the monorepo

These changes suggest ongoing maintenance and feature development in the Eliza project, with a focus on documentation updates and plugin management.
